graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        subgraph "Main Pod"
            Frontend[Frontend<br/>React 18 + TypeScript SPA<br/>PatternFly 6]
            Backend[Backend<br/>Node.js/Fastify<br/>Port 8080/TCP]
            Proxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>OAuth Sidecar<br/>Port 8443/TCP]

            Frontend -.embedded in.-> Backend
            Proxy -->|proxies to| Backend
        end

        subgraph "Modular Architecture Containers"
            ModelRegistryUI[model-registry-ui<br/>Port 8043/TCP]
            GenAIUI[gen-ai-ui<br/>Port 8143/TCP]
            MaaSUI[maas-ui<br/>Port 8243/TCP]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        OdhApplication[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhDocument[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhQuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Components"
        Operator[ODH/RHODS Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster, DSCInitialization]
        Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRD]
        KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService, ServingRuntime]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>ModelRegistry CRD]
        Feast[Feast Operator<br/>FeatureStore CRD]
        NIM[NVIDIA NIM<br/>Account CRD]
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS 443| Router[OpenShift Router]
    Router -->|HTTPS 8443<br/>TLS Reencrypt| Proxy
    Proxy -->|OAuth validation| OAuth
    Proxy -->|HTTP 8080<br/>localhost| Backend

    Backend -->|REST API<br/>ServiceAccount Token| K8sAPI
    Backend -->|Metrics queries| Prometheus
    Backend -->|creates/watches| OdhApplication
    Backend -->|manages| OdhDashboardConfig
    Backend -->|reads| OdhDocument
    Backend -->|reads| OdhQuickStart

    Backend -->|watches status| Operator
    Backend -->|creates/manages| Notebooks
    Backend -->|watches| KServe
    Backend -->|creates/manages| ModelRegistry
    Backend -->|watches| Feast
    Backend -->|manages| NIM

    Backend -->|module federation| ModelRegistryUI
    Backend -->|module federation| GenAIUI
    Backend -->|module federation| MaaSUI

    ModelRegistryUI -->|API calls| ModelRegistry

